node.text: My bride Mary Anne is a Cancer survivor. This is important, please help if you are able.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Captain Lee Rosbach on August 08, 2021 tagging @canamonroad. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: When I’m not on the water I love to get out on the open road with some friends. We took a trip across the state of Florida and back, through rain and sunshine it was a great day! Thanks @rykerrydes for showing us the ropes and @armstagram16 for flying in to make this trip. #canamonroad #canamspyder #canampartner #rykerryder #goodfriends #openroadriders #ridelikenoother
